[chuckles]

120
00:06:36,272 --> 00:06:39,855
[Shinra] Ooh, he's definitely
planning something sinister.

121
00:06:39,855 --> 00:06:40,604
Scary!

122
00:06:40,604 --> 00:06:44,397
Finally, we come back
to my better half: Celty.

123
00:06:44,397 --> 00:06:45,646
So, here's what happened:

124
00:06:45,646 --> 00:06:48,147
My stepmom came over
to clean the place,

125
00:06:48,147 --> 00:06:49,313
and then Walker showed up.

126
00:06:49,313 --> 00:06:50,896
He said something
about the apartment

127
00:06:50,896 --> 00:06:52,438
