for a secret base.

128
00:06:52,438 --> 00:06:56,563
I didn't know
what he was talking about,
so I just let him ramble on.

129
00:06:56,563 --> 00:06:58,896
Anyway, that's when
Seiji and Mika showed up,

130
00:06:58,896 --> 00:07:01,147
looking for a place to crash
for a while.

131
00:07:01,147 --> 00:07:03,896
