explain why they were here,

134
00:07:07,521 --> 00:07:10,563
and that's about the time
you came home!

135
00:07:10,563 --> 00:07:12,479
Someone tell me
what's going on!

136
00:07:12,479 --> 00:07:13,896
Um, we're putting you out.

137
00:07:13,896 --> 00:07:18,188
I think we'll go look
for another place to stay.

138
00:07:19,938 --> 00:07:23,646
