190
00:09:47,948 --> 00:09:50,948
[slow footsteps]

191
00:09:50,948 --> 00:09:54,157
-[man] Hold it right there!
-Huh?

192
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:55,823
-[gasps]
-[groans]

