a single report from you

209
00:10:50,157 --> 00:10:52,115
on any of your activities.

210
00:10:52,115 --> 00:10:54,740
-[grunts]
-[Egor] Uh-oh. Shingen?

211
00:10:54,740 --> 00:10:57,032
[Eijiro] We should get
while the getting's good.

212
00:10:57,032 --> 00:11:01,157
