Gas Mask Two and Three!

213
00:11:01,157 --> 00:11:02,573
[gasps, groans]

214
00:11:02,573 --> 00:11:04,198
-[Shingen] We'll meet again!
-[coughing]

215
00:11:04,198 --> 00:11:08,198
