00:21:54,906 --> 00:21:57,531
[Shinra]
The woman I love is caught up
in something big,

474
00:21:57,531 --> 00:22:00,115
and I'm going to help
get her out.

475
00:22:00,115 --> 00:22:04,823
Don't worry, Celty.
I'll be here to help you.

476
00:22:06,781 --> 00:22:07,990
All right.

477
00:22:07,990 --> 00:22:09,906
If everyone's fine with it,
so am I.

478
00:22:09,906 --> 00:22:13,990
[chuckles]
Ladies and gentlemen,
we're a guild!

479
00:22:13,990 --> 00:22:15,489
[Shinra]
And now, as a team,

480
00:22:15,489 --> 00:22:17,282
we have a chance
to get to the person

481
00:22:17,282 --> 00:22:19,656
who's responsible
for all of our troubles.

482
00:22:19,656 --> 00:22:23,656
Whoever it is,
we're going to get them.

483
00:22:23,656 --> 00:22:25,823
Count on it!

484
00:22:26,448 --> 00:22:30,198
[theme song playing]

485
00:23:55,073 --> 00:23:59,032
[Shingen]
Let's talk about women
for a second.

486
00:23:59,032 --> 00:24:00,282
All kinds of women.

487
00:24:00,282 --> 00:24:02,240
Suffering women,
powerful women,

488
00:24:02,240 --> 00:24:05,032
warrior women,
sneaky, conniving women.

489
00:24:05,032 --> 00:24:09,740
Next time: Bell the Cat.
Women will be women.

